{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely radio, without labels, texts nor icons radios components","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSRadio","roleHeading":"Structure","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","text":"Particular cases","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDSThemesContract side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","text":"Cases forbidden by design","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}]},{"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button"}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","level":2},{"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","text":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radio_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading","text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","text":"Sosh","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Sosh"}]},{"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","text":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Wireframe"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.3.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Version"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"]},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio\/body"]},{"anchor":"De